The riddle is a trick; the premise is false. Succubi are **not** more common than perceived, nor are they the "better choice" for most leveling due to their high mana cost and fragility. Voidwalkers are preferred for their tankiness and self-sustain (Soul Leech). The hint is misleading; Succubi do not have a skill that makes them "more common than perceived." In fact, Voidwalkers are the most commonly seen demon because they are the first demon learned and are superior for solo survivability. [end of text]


